---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="E-commerce Development Guide | Store">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <img 
      src="/images/blog/ecom-blog.jpg" 
      alt="E-commerce Development"
      class="w-full aspect-video object-cover rounded-2xl mb-8 shadow-lg"
    />

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <time>November 29, 2023</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-gray-300 rounded-full"></span>
        <span>8 min read</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-gray-300 rounded-full"></span>
        <span>Development</span>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Building a Modern E-commerce Platform</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          A comprehensive guide to creating scalable online stores using Astro.js, TypeScript, and modern web technologies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 my-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Quick Overview</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Tech Stack</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                Astro.js for performance
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                TypeScript for type safety
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                Tailwind CSS for styling
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Key Features</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                Dynamic cart system
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                Category filtering
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                Responsive design
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Modern Development Approach</h2>
        <p>
          Our e-commerce template leverages Astro.js's powerful static site generation capabilities, delivering lightning-fast page loads and optimal performance. Combined with TypeScript's robust type system, we ensure a development experience that's both productive and maintainable.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Performance & User Experience</h2>
        <p>
          Every aspect of the platform is optimized for speed and usability. From the responsive product grid to the seamless cart interactions, we've crafted an experience that feels natural and engaging on any device.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Future-Ready Architecture</h2>
        <p>
          Built with scalability in mind, our template provides a solid foundation for growth. Whether you're launching a small boutique or planning for larger scale operations, the architecture adapts to your needs.
        </p>

        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 mt-12 pt-8">
          <a 
            href="/blog" 
            class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-black transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
            </svg>
            Back to Blog
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
.prose {
  max-width: none;
}
.prose h2 {
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.3;
}
.prose p {
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: #374151;
}
</style>
